Package: lintrhelper
Type: Package
Title: Create Custom Lintr Rules Without XPath Knowledge
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Fabian", "Distler",
    email = "fabiandistler@users.noreply.github.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Simplifies the creation of custom linters for the 'lintr' package
    without requiring XPath or XML knowledge. Provides high-level functions to
    forbid symbols, ban functions, enforce naming conventions, require specific
    arguments, and more. Also includes XPath-based builders for advanced users,
    testing utilities, and ready-to-use example linters.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
